{"tid":1894524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利增至3死共152人確診","createTime":"2020-02-24T03:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T03:54:52.000Z","uid":241764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30472fd8d27e70cdb86fa2b98b7b76c0d29073a5","tid":1894524,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情在意大利急速擴散，當地累計確診病例增至152宗。衛生官員周日（23日）表示，一名感染新型冠狀病毒、患癌的年長女子死亡，意大利累計死亡人數增至3人。該名女子在倫巴第（Lombardy）城市克雷馬（Crema）一間醫院離世，倫巴第大區衛生局長加勒拉（Giulio Gallera）稱，該名女子曾住院數天，現時判斷她的主要死因是病毒仍言之尚早。<br />\n<br />\n總理孔特呼籲民眾不要恐慌，「我們不應該對上升數字感到害怕」，稱確診病例飇升是因為進行數以千計檢測。<br />\n <img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200224/s00005/92caaf4a010b573411cb2f1797ea2452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200224%2Fs00005%2F92caaf4a010b573411cb2f1797ea2452.jpg&h=afb8f436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200224/s00005/1582511892669/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%84%8f%e5%a4%a7%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e8%87%b33%e6%ad%bb%e5%85%b1152%e4%ba%ba%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200224%2Fs00005%2F1582511892669%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2584%258f%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2588%25a9%25e5%25a2%259e%25e8%2587%25b33%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e5%2585%25b1152%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=42a01792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200224%2Fs00005%2F1582511892669%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2584%258f%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%2588%25a9%25e5%25a2%259e%25e8%2587%25b33%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e5%2585%25b1152%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%25a2%2